- Well I was going to ask you that.

00:02:23.891 --> 00:02:24.993
- Steve certainly did.

00:02:24.993 --> 00:02:26.946
- Steve, did you feel that, did you feel

00:02:26.946 --> 00:02:28.287
the same atmosphere in
your house growing up,

00:02:28.287 --> 00:02:30.020
that the Ambassador just--

